fields.question: Are you able to make and receive calls?
fields.subtext: Check your device for cellular network connectivity issues.

fields.question: Is your device's touch screen working properly?
fields.subtext: Check the touch screen functionality of your phone.

fields.question: Is your phone's screen original?
fields.subtext: Pick "Yes" if screen was never changed or was changed by Authorized Service Center. Pick "No" if screen was changed at local shop.

fields.question: Is your device under brand warranty?
fields.subtext: You can get a better price for your device if it's under brand's warranty with a valid bill.

fields.question: Do you have valid bill with same IMEI?
fields.subtext: Make sure your bill has device IMEI mentioned on it.
